果個歲數就需要果啲野，<br />\n好似死神頭果part, 基本上成個concep 係幽游前期+星矢十二宮，<br />\ngundam seed 直情將之前高達hit 嘅元素全部翻炒一次（戲軌，機設，人設...)<br />\n<br />\n你睇過前作舊作，咪覺得佢低能鳩抄，<br />\n但係新生代第一次接觸就會覺得超正好能正，<br />\n繼而成為佢地生命中嘅經典（等如你嘅星矢，0079)<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係而家3,4千蚊一隻SF ,00R 果啲搵邊個買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正如有好多人唔理幾錢都要買新雙子一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01a9f84082f6b98644cd7b651c4ac5fb776ec7c","tid":182754,"uid":77760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:35:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇下one老師啲分鏡<br />\n再睇下東京食屍鬼啲分鏡<br />\n<br />\n睇下one老師啲角色<br />\n再睇下巨人同食屍鬼啲角色樣</blockquote><br />\nOne分鏡係高汁<br />\n<br />\n西瓜就畫靚，但一畫打就on99<br />\n不過勝在人物描寫犀利，又有文學味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n東京食屎狗文戲既分鏡係冇問題<br />\n<br />\n係一到打鬥場面就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於One 佢既分鏡係幾高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cdb6f35fccccb8cef4dae813a9128daf68ec400","tid":182754,"uid":32516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:12:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇下one老師啲分鏡<br />\n再睇下東京食屍鬼啲分鏡<br />\n<br />\n睇下one老師啲角色<br />\n再睇下巨人同食屍鬼啲角色樣</blockquote><br />\nOne分鏡係高汁<br />\n<br />\n西瓜就畫靚，但一畫打就on99<br />\n不過勝在人物描寫犀利，又有文學味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n東京食屎狗文戲既分鏡係冇問題<br />\n<br />\n係一到打鬥場面就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於One 佢既分鏡係幾高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsorry我應該講明打鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370c1cb1ddfbc05334ede6ec6e6fe65c11704955","tid":182754,"uid":861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ph0nx9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F